"1/2 cup 2% reduced-fat Greek yogurt","1/4 cup clam juice","2 tablespoons lemon juice","1  (8-ounce) package 1/3-less-fat cream cheese, softened","1/4 cup chopped chives","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","3  (6.5-ounce) cans chopped clams, drained","2  fennel bulbs, trimmed and cut into 1/4-inch-thick wedges","8 ounces mini bell peppers, quartered lengthwise"